data.description: Welcome home! 4 bedroom/2.5 bath house invites you into the 2-story foyer with bonus room, formal dining room with beautiful molding, kitchen that opens to family room with stacked stone fireplace. The kitchen has upgraded granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, an island, and eat-in breakfast area. Upstairs you find 4 bedrooms and 2 remolded bathrooms. Master bedroom has a rain shower, soaking tub, his and her vanities, and huge walk-in closet with safe. The oversized master bedroom had trey ceilings, large sitting area for relaxing or workspace. Outside you will find a well-maintained, landscaped backyard with pergola over a patio. Extra gazebo allows for enjoying the private yard that backs up to a bird sanctuary. Fenced backyard is ready for pets! The neighborhood has pool and playground included in low HOA fee. Close to schools, retail shops, and grocery stores. Easy access to 575! Appraisal has been done, and price reflects appraisal.
